The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the full complexity of the relationship between failure and success. Additionally, the examples provided are anecdotal and may not be universally applicable. Further research, including empirical studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of how failure leads to success.

